import React, { FC } from 'react' import { Food } from '../type' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { OrderDelete } from '../store/menuSlice' interface ItemOrderType { product : Food } const ItemOrder:FC =({product}) => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const deleteItem = (product:Food):void => { dispatch(OrderDelete(product)) } return (

{product.food_name}

{product.food_price}

) } export default ItemOrder
